Key Match Events: Shadab (2/16) and Shaheen Shah Afridi (3/14) blew away the South African top order
Tristan Stubbs (18) and Heinrich Klaasen (15) came all guns blazing under the pump
Shadheen forced an inside edge to claim South Africa's fifth wicket
South Africa needed 73 off five overs
Post-Match Reflections: Pakistan (4 points) moved up to the third spot in group 2
South Africa (5 points) continued to stay second behind leaders India (6 points)
Miscellaneous Highlights: Pakistan lost an early wicket in Mohammed Rizwan
Anrich Nortje was the most successful bowler for South Africa with figures of 4/41
